316
00:15:20,827 --> 00:15:25,793
Soon that Ranma Saotome will
be in the palm of my hand.

317
00:15:25,827 --> 00:15:28,493
And then I'll have
Akane Tendo too.

318
00:15:28,527 --> 00:15:32,027
Not to mention the
pigtailed girl.

319
00:15:32,060 --> 00:15:35,660
[maniacal laughter]

320
00:15:35,693 --> 00:15:37,960
[rumbling]

321
00:15:42,727 --> 00:15:43,660
-What is that?

322
00:15:43,693 --> 00:15:46,060
-It's a pillar of cats.

323
00:15:46,093 --> 00:15:47,360
-Look there.

324
00:15:47,393 --> 00:15:48,093
It's Akane Tendo.

325
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:53,460
Here, my love.

326
00:15:53,493 --> 00:15:55,227
-Oh, this is so sudden, Master.

327
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:01,360
-Not you, fool.

328
00:16:01,393 --> 00:16:03,560
My darling Akane.

329
00:16:03,593 --> 00:16:04,527
Oh, my love.

330
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:14,760
Oof-- Get off me, you beast.

331
00:16:14,793 --> 00:16:16,260
Have you gone mad?

332
00:16:25,227 --> 00:16:25,860
-Hah!

333
00:16:25,893 --> 00:16:27,827
