343
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:56,527
-Words can't reach
Ranma right now.

344
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:57,593
-How come?

345
00:16:57,627 --> 00:16:58,160
Why?

346
00:16:58,193 --> 00:16:59,460
What can we do?

347
00:16:59,493 --> 00:17:02,393
-So it was an omen after all.

348
00:17:02,427 --> 00:17:04,060
-What do you mean
words can't reach him.

349
00:17:04,093 --> 00:17:05,060
What's wrong with him?

350
00:17:05,093 --> 00:17:06,627
Is he sick or something?

351
00:17:06,660 --> 00:17:11,893
-When Ranma's acute fear of cats
goes beyond a certain point,

352
00:17:11,927 --> 00:17:14,127
the only way for him
to deal with that fear

353
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,793
is to become a cat himself.

354
00:17:15,827 --> 00:17:18,327
[meow]

355
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:20,260
Only one person
can reach him when

356
00:17:20,293 --> 00:17:22,793
he's like this-- a
