one of his better ideas.

371
00:18:04,793 --> 00:18:06,660
Catnip?

372
00:18:06,693 --> 00:18:08,260
-Don't worry, Ranma.

373
00:18:08,293 --> 00:18:09,660
I forgive you.

374
00:18:21,993 --> 00:18:24,293
-It looks like he's
getting worse, dad.

375
00:18:24,327 --> 00:18:25,860
