376
00:18:25,893 --> 00:18:26,560
-Don't worry.

377
00:18:26,593 --> 00:18:27,793
Leave everything to me.

378
00:18:27,827 --> 00:18:28,760
-You?

379
00:18:28,793 --> 00:18:30,960
-All cats love
catnip, don't they?

